Caption by: Luis Miguel Rubinos
Pubmat by: JM Pastores

𝑬𝒎𝒂𝒊𝒍𝒔 𝒉𝒂𝒗𝒆 𝒃𝒆𝒆𝒏 𝒔𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝒃𝒚 𝑺𝒏𝒐𝒐𝒑𝒚!

The 𝑷𝒂𝒍𝒂𝒘𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑬𝒙𝒑𝒓𝒆𝒔𝒔 deliveries have been sent to our 𝑭𝑬𝑼 𝑬𝑳𝑪 𝒂𝒑𝒑𝒍𝒊𝒄𝒂𝒏𝒕𝒔! Kindly 𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐜𝐤 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐩𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐨𝐮𝐭𝐥𝐨𝐨𝐤 𝐞𝐦𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐬 to learn about the results of your application.

Kindly 𝒓𝒆𝒑𝒍𝒚 𝒕𝒐 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒆𝒎𝒂𝒊𝒍 by acknowledging that you have received it 𝐛𝐞𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐞 𝟓 𝐏𝐌, 𝐭𝐨𝐝𝐚𝐲.

We would like to congratulate our ELC applicants for braving the application process! May you be the pieces that allow us to continue #PiecingByDesign.

Pubmat by: JM Pastores
